      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your feelings of exhaustion are valid, but believing that leaving would bring peace is a dangerous thought that ignores the deep bonds you share. It is not fair to your family to assume their lives would be better if you were gone, as your presence and history are part of their reality. Please consider speaking with a mental health professional who can help you navigate these intense emotions and find ways to cope without harming yourself.",
      "source": "target",
